NUMBER 1780
CHANNEL 82
DEEPCAVE
MONSTER_GROUP 41
FIXED_LIGHT
MINEB
REGION 2
NAME Deep Realms, caves
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This cave is crowded by ancient stalagmites and stalactites that have joined as one, forming great limestone columns. Phosphorescent fungus clings to the walls, casting a subdued blue illumination over everything.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NE 1779
EXIT W 1781
EXIT SE 1783
ITEM 0 327
ITEM 1 1509 ADJ1=1110
ITEM 2 336
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The fungus appears to absorbed some chemicals from the surrounding bedrock that have granted it this strange phosphorescent quality. You could probably tear off a small amount for yourself, but it wouldn't be enough to light your way.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Upon closer inspection, you notice that there is a hole near the top of one of the columns. Although the surface of the limestone is smooth, you might be able to shimmy you way up to it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB CLIMB 1
	CLEARVERB
	EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
	SKILLCHECK 5 0 DUMMY1
	IFVAR DUMMY1 >= 0
		ECHO PLAYER You shimmy up the column.
		ECHO OTHERS %N shimmies up the column.
		MOVE 1788
		AFFECT 1788
		ECHO OTHERS %N shimmies up the column and up through the hole in the ground.
		AFFECT 1780
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER You start to climb a column, but loose your grip and slide down halfway up.
                ECHO OTHERS %N starts to climb up a column, but loses %h grip and slides down halfway up.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 2
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER You'll have to climb the column if you want to go through the hole.
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 2
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER You can't reach the hole.
ENDIF
IFVERB TAP 2
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER You can't reach the hole.
ENDIF
IFVERB TOUCH 0
	ECHO PLAYER The fungus feels soft and spongy, soaking up moisture that seeps from the rocks above.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GET 0
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR FUNGUSTIM ! TIM
		NEWITEM 3 1441 ADJ1=145 VAL2=3 VAL3=313 VAL5=11
		ECHO PLAYER You pull on the fungus, and a small bunch falls on the cave floor.
		ECHO OTHERS %N tears off a small piece of glowing fungus.
		EQUAL FUNGUSTIM TIM
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER It appears that the fungus has been harvested recently. Maybe you could try and get some again, when it has had a little time to grow.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
