MONSTER_GROUP 43
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The cavern is filled with mushrooms. Huge mushrooms. They resemble multicolored
trees, and the canopy made by their outspreading caps forms an organic ceiling
high overhead. The cavern floor is covered with broken fungal stalks like the
remains of shattered pillars, held up at odd angles by the floor itself: a
sludge composed of gray and brown decayed matter, mostly mud but with many
other elements. A few splinters of dry white bone lie imbedded in this
surface, protruding like the arms of drowning men. The warm air coursing
down the cliff face does nothing to dispel the humidity which makes you
feel sticky and uncomfortable. A fairly new tunnel leads northeast.
*DESCRIPTION_END
DARKNESS
DEEPCAVE
CHANNEL 82
IFVERB SMELL -1
	ECHO PLAYER You smell a musty odor, revolting in its richness.
ENDIF
