NUMBER 1356
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS
MINEB
CHANNEL 82
REGION 2
NAME Devil's chimney
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are at the bottom of a long natural shaft. There is not much room here to move about. Your choices are limited to climbing up the craggy wall or squeezing out out a small crevice.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 83 VAL2=1357
ITEM 1 427
IFPREVERB GO 1
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR ROUNDTIME > 0
		STRCVT 0 ROUNDTIME
		ECHO PLAYER [Wait %0 seconds...]
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ROUNDTIME = 0
		IFVAR CRACKOPEN = 1
			ECHO PLAYER Someone else is blocking the crevice right now.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CRACKOPEN = 0
			EQUAL ROUNDTIME 6
			ECHO PLAYER You begin to squeeze through the crevice.
			ECHO OTHERS %N begins to squeeze through the crevice.
			EQUAL CRACKOPEN 1
			PLREVENT 2
			CONTPLREVENT
			RANDOM DUMMY1 1 60 0
			EQUAL CRACKOPEN 0
			ADD DUMMY1 HEI
			IFVAR DUMMY1 < 100
				ECHO PLAYER After a few moments struggle, you finally squeeze through.
				ECHO OTHERS After a few moments struggle, %n finally squeezes through the crevice.
				MOVE 1600
				AFFECT 1600
				SHOWROOM 1600
				ECHO OTHERS %N comes out of a crevice.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY1 > 99
				IFVAR DUMMY1 < 120
					ECHO PLAYER Your height causes you a bit of trouble but after a few moments struggle, you finally squeeze through with a "pop".
					ECHO OTHERS After a few moments struggle, %n finally squeezes through the crevice.
					MOVE 1600
					AFFECT 1600
					SHOWROOM 1600
					ECHO OTHERS %N comes out of a crevice with an audible "pop!"
				ENDIF
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY1 > 119
				ECHO PLAYER You are unable to get through the crevice, and you step away.
				ECHO OTHERS %N just can't get through the crevice and steps away.
				AFFECT 1600
				ECHO ALL You hear a groan from the other side of the crevice as someone fails to squeeze through.
			ENDIF
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
